### 1️⃣ Save Token
POST http://localhost:5000/save-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "User Satu",
  "fcm_device_token": "YOUR_FCM_DEVICE_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### 2️⃣ Get All Tokens
GET http://localhost:5000/all-data

### 3️⃣ Send Notification by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/send-notification/1

### 4️⃣ Send Custom Notification
POST http://localhost:5000/send-notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "YOUR_FCM_DEVICE_TOKEN_HERE",
  "title": "Judul Notif",
  "body": "Ini notifikasi custom dari API",
  "data": {
    "redirect": "/dashboard",
    "type": "announcement",
    "user_id": "12345"
  }
}

### 5️⃣ Delete User by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/delete-data/1
